        <h4 style="font-weight: normal">The main goal of this part was to discover primary challenges companies commonly face. I created a <strong>questionaire</strong> for an employees from 5 international companies. I also <strong>interviewed</strong> HR people and managers from 3 international companies with over 100 employees. The goal was to find out the best practices of their program and tools they are using.  </h3>
        <h4 style="font-weight: normal">Based on the research I created two <strong>personas</strong> which representing different type of leaders. It provided me different perspective on how the program should be created depending on the needs of the company and personality of their leaders.  </h4>
            
